1. Navigated to the alx-intermediate-frontend repository:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

2. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using nvm:
   a. curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   b. Restarted the terminal.
   c. Installed Node.js:
      nvm install 20.16
      nvm use 20.16
   d. Verified Node.js version:
      node -v

3. Installed SASS version 3.7.4:
   npm install sass@3.7.4
